Zbiór multimodal-sparse¶

In [3]:
df = pd.read_csv("./data/regression/multimodal-sparse-training.csv")
X = df.x.to_numpy()
X = np.transpose(np.array([X]))
Y = df.y.to_numpy()
Y = np.transpose(np.array([Y]))

df1 = pd.read_csv("./data/regression/multimodal-sparse-test.csv")
X1 = df1.x.to_numpy()
X1 = np.transpose(np.array([X1]))
Y1 = df1.y.to_numpy()
Y1 = np.transpose(np.array([Y1]))

Testowanie dla regularyzacji L1¶

In [ ]:
results_l1 = []
In [ ]:
for lambda_ in lambdas:
    print(f"Training for lambda = {lambda_}")
    np.random.seed(0)
    model = Net(optimizer = SGD_regularised(learning_rate=0.00001, regularization=RegularizationL1(lambda_)))
    model.add_layer(DenseNetLayer(1, 100, ReLU(), RandomNormalInitializer()))
    model.add_layer(DenseNetLayer(100, 20, ReLU(), RandomNormalInitializer()))
    model.add_layer(DenseNetLayer(20, 1, LinearFunction(), RandomNormalInitializer()))
    model.train(X, Y, X1, Y1, n_epochs=2000, eval_frequency=100, early_stop=100)

    model.save_model('./' + 'multimodal-sparse-' + str(lambda_) + '-l1.model')
    results_l1.append(mse(Y1, model.forward(X1)))

    model = Net(optimizer = SGD_regularised(learning_rate=0.00001, regularization=RegularizationL1(lambda_)))

for lambda_ in lambdas:
    print(f"Training for lambda = {lambda_}")
    np.random.seed(0)
    model = Net(optimizer = SGD_regularised(learning_rate=0.00001, regularization=RegularizationL2(lambda_)))
    model.add_layer(DenseNetLayer(1, 100, ReLU(), RandomNormalInitializer()))
    model.add_layer(DenseNetLayer(100, 20, ReLU(), RandomNormalInitializer()))
    model.add_layer(DenseNetLayer(20, 1, LinearFunction(), RandomNormalInitializer()))
    model.train(X, Y, X1, Y1, n_epochs=2000, eval_frequency=100, early_stop=100)

    model.save_model('./' + 'multimodal-sparse-' + str(lambda_) + '-l2.model')
    results_l2.append(mse(Y1, model.forward(X1)))

for lambda_ in lambdas:
    print(f"Continuing training for lambda = {lambda_}")
    np.random.seed(0)
    model = Net(optimizer = SGD_regularised(learning_rate=0.00001, regularization=RegularizationL2(lambda_)))
    model.add_layer(DenseNetLayer(1, 100, ReLU(), RandomNormalInitializer()))
    model.add_layer(DenseNetLayer(100, 20, ReLU(), RandomNormalInitializer()))
    model.add_layer(DenseNetLayer(20, 1, LinearFunction(), RandomNormalInitializer()))

    model.load_model('./' + 'multimodal-sparse-' + str(lambda_) + '-l2.model')
    model.train(X, Y, X1, Y1, n_epochs=2000, eval_frequency=100, early_stop=100)

    model.save_model('./' + 'multimodal-sparse-' + str(lambda_) + '-l2-continued.model')
    results_l2_continued.append(mse(Y1, model.forward(X1)))

In [6]:
for lambda_ in lambdas:
    print(f"Training for lambda = {lambda_}")
    np.random.seed(0)
    model = Net(optimizer = SGD_regularised(learning_rate=0.0001, regularization=RegularizationL1(lambda_)), loss = 'cross-entropy')
    model.add_layer(DenseNetLayer(2, 20, ReLU(), XavierInitializer(2, 20)))
    model.add_layer(DenseNetLayer(20, 20, ReLU(), XavierInitializer(20, 20)))
    model.add_layer(DenseNetLayer(20, 5, SoftmaxAsLastLayerWithCrossEntropy(), XavierInitializer(20, 5)))
    model.train(X, Y, X1, Y1, n_epochs=2000, eval_frequency=100, early_stop=100)

    model.save_model('./' + 'rings5-sparse-' + str(lambda_) + '-l1.model')
    results_l1.append(cross_entropy(Y1, model.forward(X1)))

Testowanie dla regularyzacji L1¶

In [6]:
results_l1 = []
In [8]:
for lambda_ in lambdas:
    print(f"Training for lambda = {lambda_}")
    np.random.seed(0)
    model = Net(optimizer = SGD_regularised(learning_rate=0.0001, regularization=RegularizationL1(lambda_)), loss = 'cross-entropy')
    model.add_layer(DenseNetLayer(2, 20, ReLU(), XavierInitializer(2, 20)))
    model.add_layer(DenseNetLayer(20, 20, ReLU(), XavierInitializer(20, 20)))
    model.add_layer(DenseNetLayer(20, 3, SoftmaxAsLastLayerWithCrossEntropy(), XavierInitializer(20, 3)))
    model.train(X, Y, X1, Y1, n_epochs=2000, eval_frequency=100, early_stop=100)

    model.save_model('./' + 'rings3-balance-' + str(lambda_) + '-l1.model')
    results_l1.append(cross_entropy(Y1, model.forward(X1)))
